==English==

===Noun===

{{en-noun}}

# {{Manorial}} A person ranking below [[villein]]s and above [[serf]]s in the social hierarchy of a [[manor]], holding just enough land to feed a family (about 5 acres) and required to provide labour on the [[demesne]] on specified days of the week .

